Gana nye [[Afrika]] dukɔwo dometɔ ɖeka. Ele [[Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe]] lɔƒo. Gana do liƒo kple [[Togo]] kple , [[Nyiɖu Ƒuta]] kpakple [[Burkina Faso]]. Aƒu si woyɔna be ''[[Gulf of Guinea]]'' la le eƒe anyiehe lɔƒo. Eƒe dukɔmenɔlawo ƒe xexlẽme ɖo 22,113,000 lɔƒo.
Woɖo Gana tso ''Gold Coast'' kpakple ''British Togoland'' si nɔ Fransetɔwo ƒe dziɖuɖu te la ƒe kpekpe me. Gana dukɔa xɔ dokuisinɔnɔ tso Eŋlisiawo gbɔ le Tedoxe 6 dzi, le ƒe 1957 me. Ghana ƒe fiadzue nye [[Accra]].

== Dukplɔlawo ==

Gana ƒe dukplɔla enye [[John Dramani Mahama]]. Ele dziɖum tso Dzome 7, 2012. Eƒe kpeɖeŋutɔ enye Amissah Arthur.

== Nutuwo ==

Nuto ewoe (10) le Gana. 

